<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Please update the RewriteRouter documentation in the incubator, in the Zend_Controller-Provided_Subclasses.xml file, to reflect current usage. Examples in there show the following notation:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$router-&gt;addRoute('user', ':controller/:action);
</code></pre>

<p>which should actually be:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$router-&gt;addRoute(
    new Zend_Controller_Router_Route('user', ':controller/:action')
);
</code></pre>

    </div>
</div>

